{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6006", "repo": "rails", "body": "@carlosantoniodasilva , i'm not sure about responsibility, anyway adding tag  could make much reusable the partial_view.\r\n\r\nfor example , if you have a partial:\r\n```erb\r\n<span><%=post.autor%></span>\r\n<span><%=post.created_at%></span>\r\n``` \r\nyou could render inside two different tags\r\n\r\n```erb\r\n<ul>\r\n<%= render @posts,:tag=>'li'%>\r\n</ul>\r\n```\r\noutput:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n <span>one</span> \r\n <span>Tomorrow</span>\r\n </li>\r\n\r\n<li>\r\n <span>two</span> \r\n <span>Today</span>\r\n </li>\r\n</ul> \r\n```\r\nor\r\n\r\n```erb\r\n<div>\r\n<%= render @posts,:tag=>'div'%>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\noutput:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n <span>one</span> \r\n <span>Tomorrow</span>\r\n </div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n <span>two</span> \r\n <span>Today</span>\r\n </div>\r\n</div> \r\n\r\n```\r\nSorry, it just a simple idea :)\r\n", "_id": {"$oid": "52381041bd3543c15100d635"}, "issue_id": 6006, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5380270", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6006#issuecomment-5380270", "updated_at": "2012-04-28T06:12:58Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri", "login": "acapilleri", "gravatar_id": "0cd98f4e263d306bc455ca750c31443f", "html_url": "https://github.com/acapilleri", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/0cd98f4e263d306bc455ca750c31443f?d=htt